markdownRemark.html: Last month, I had the privilege of flying to Seattle and attending TSConf, a one-day single-track conference all about TypeScript! I want to share some of my key takeaways and what I’m excited about going forward.

frontmatter.title: Top Takeways from TSConf
frontmatter.description: Key takeaways, what I’m excited about going forward, and a comfy pair of socks.
